Package: tibblesummary
Type: Package
Title: Summary Functions for the Tidyverse
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lars Steggink <contact@larssteggink.nl>
Maintainer: Lars Steggink <contact@larssteggink.nl>
Description: These are simple functions combining the powers of the tidyverse to quickly create summary statistics and summary graphs for multiple variables of a tibble or data frame at once, using the standard selectors available in dplyr.
